name: Cathay Pacific Cargo 747-867F [B-LJB] INAUGURAL Landing at Calgary Airport ᴴᴰ
description:
Welcome to YYC, Cathay Pacific Cargo! Here we have B-LJB, one of Cathay Pacific Cargo's 747-8F aircraft arriving for the very first time today on Runway 35L at Calgary International Airport, and, much to the joy of the YYC spotting community, in daylight and some beautiful morning lighting. This new service will be operating twice a week, on Tuesdays/Wednesdays and Fridays/Saturdays. Stick around to the end of the video to see the water salute! I hope you enjoy, and watch in HD.

Thanks for watching! Please comment, rate, and subscribe!
